# scenarios/

Demo scenario scripts + recordings. Five scenarios per the plan's Sprint 3 /
Sprint 3.5 gates:

- `01-resume-fill.md`              (Form persona)
- `02-meeting-notes.md`            (Authoring persona)
- `03-one-page-report.md`          (Authoring persona)
- `04-bulk-official-letters.md`    (Form persona)
- `05-hwp-to-hwpx-roundtrip.md`    (Compatibility persona)

`recordings/` holds the screen captures referenced by Sprint exit criteria.
